metadata.name: Harvesting corn into the flood water
metadata.description:
Cornfields are submerged in water after a deadly flood devastated the area. Farmers trying to salvage as much as they can from fields destroyed by the annual disaster. Thousands of hectares of cornfields were swamped by the flood in Sariakandi, Bogura, Bangladesh.

Details ~
Artist: Azim Khan Ronnie

Location: Bangladesh/2020
